title: #92Noon! PP/Wild/Leber/Birk/Sando
description: We're pumped about adding Patrick Peterson to the Vikings and how the defense is shaping up...that takes most of the first hour. More football with Leber and Birk over the final two hours, and the show wraps with tremendous football writer(The Athletic) Mike Sando!
